### Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe the problem.

I am trying to get absolute path for the current user's `Downloads` directory. Currently the easiest way for me to do this is with the following code:

```
var path = Path.GetDirectoryName(Environment.GetFolderPath(Environment.SpecialFolder.Personal));
// C:\Users\jason\OneDrive
var downloadsPath = Path.Combine(Directory.GetParent(path), "Downloads");
// C:\Users\jason\Downloads <-- desired value
```



